      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        The Fiscal Trap: James Lavish on Why Bitcoin Is the Only Rational Exit From a Debasing Dollar
      </h1>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-400 text-sm border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
        <span>Lisa Tamati</span>
        <span class="text-white/20">|</span>
        <span>18/04/2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
      <img
